item.dc:creator: @magep00ner12 magep00ner12
item.description:
@magep00ner12 wrote:

[quote=“supra s, post:2, topic:169404”]mmh your dutch ^.^

English : you need to check what the current jdk versions is go look at C:\Program Files\Java

then right clickon your compiler.bat end open in notepad delete everything inside end replace it with this :

@echo off "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause(jdk1.6.0_03 chage it to your version)

nederlands; kijk welke versie je hebt van jdk doe dit op C:\Program Files\Java

derna rechter muiskilik op je compiler.bat en open in kladblok alles wat er staat delete en vervangen me dit:

@echo off "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause(jdk1.6.0_03 verandere me jouw versie)

good luck
veel geluk[/quote]
